<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-4">
            <img src="~/images/ok.png" class="img-fluid" alt="Image" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-8">
            <div data-bs-spy="scroll" data-bs-target="#list-example" data-bs-offset="0" data-bs-smooth-scroll="true" class="scrollspy-example">
                <section id="list-item-1">
                    <h2>Release Introduction: Smart Manager - Your Work Management Solution</h2>
                    <p>
                        We are excited to introduce Smart Manager, a powerful and intuitive ASP.NET Core MVC application designed to streamline your work management process. Whether you're an individual professional, a small business, or a team, Smart Manager empowers you to efficiently import, organize, and manage your work data with ease.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section id="list-item-2">
                    <h2>Key Features</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Data Import from Excel: Smart Manager makes it effortless to import data from Excel files. Simply upload your Excel spreadsheets, and the application will automatically parse and save the data into a structured database, saving you time and effort.</li>
                        <li>Effortless Work Management: With an intuitive user interface, you can easily manage your data. Edit, add, or remove records seamlessly. Smart Manager provides you with a clean and organized workspace to keep your data up to date.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                <section id="list-item-3">
                    <h2>User-Friendly Dashboard</h2>
                    <p>
                        Our user interface is designed for maximum usability. You'll find it easy to navigate, even if you're not a tech expert. All your essential tools and options are conveniently located at your fingertips.
                    </p>
                    <h2>Customizable Work Categories</h2>
                    <p>
                        Tailor your work categories to fit your specific needs. Smart Manager is adaptable and lets you create custom fields to suit your unique workflow.
                    </p>
                    <h2>Data Visualization</h2>
                    <p>
                        Gain insights into your work with insightful charts and graphs. Understand your data at a glance, and make informed decisions to improve your productivity.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section id="list-item-4">
                    <h2>Export Data</h2>
                    <p>
                        Smart Manager allows you to export your data back to Excel or other popular formats for further analysis or sharing with your team.
                    </p>
                    <h2>Secure and Reliable</h2>
                    <p>
                        Your data is precious, and Smart Manager takes its security seriously. Rest assured that your information is stored securely and reliably.
                    </p>
                    <h2>Get Started Today</h2>
                    <p>
                        With Smart Manager, you have the tools you need to efficiently manage your work, streamline your processes, and make data-driven decisions. Say goodbye to manual data entry and hello to smarter work management.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


